<1ST_LINE>a e BC-WKD--Ameche ADV11-13   10-31 0828</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>BC-WKD--Ameche, ADV 11-13,0846</2ND_LINE>
<NOTE>$Adv11</NOTE>
