<1ST_LINE>a e BC-WKD--Zimerman ADV11-13   10-31 0957</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>BC-WKD--Zimerman, ADV 11-13,1000</2ND_LINE>
<NOTE>$Adv11</NOTE>
