<FILEID>AP-NR-10-31-88 1608EST</FILEID>
<1ST_LINE>u f PM-WallStreet355pm     10-31 0036</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>PM-Wall Street 355pm,0041</2ND_LINE>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Stock prices drifted slightly lower in quiet
trading today.
   Five minutes before the close, the Dow Jones average of 30
industrials was down 1.95 points at 2,147.94.
